  "ComponentID": "W25Q128JV",
  "ComponentType": "Serial Flash Memory (SPI NOR Flash)",
  "Description": "The W25Q128JV is a 3V, 128‑megabit (16‑megabyte) serial flash memory that supports standard SPI, Dual SPI, and Quad SPI interfaces for high‑speed data transfer. It is designed for code shadowing, execute‑in‑place (XIP), and data storage in space‑constrained systems. The memory is organized into 65,536 pages of 256 bytes each, with flexible erase options (4KB sector, 32KB/64KB block, or full chip erase). It operates from a single 2.7‑3.6V supply, features low‑power modes, and includes software/hardware write protection, security registers, and configurable status registers.",
